        & a brief throwback to 1985: around this time that year is when whitney houston was starting to become a huge pop star!  her first big hit 'you give good love' was becoming huge on mtv & on the radio around this time that year *she had a few other singles come out before that one, but none of them did anything* & then by the end of 1985 'how will i know' was a huge hit over here!  that's around the time i bought her album...&i gotta tell you guys, that was something!  seeing her go from nothing & blowing up that year & then even bigger with the bodyguard soundtrack in 1992.  all that year, you couldn't miss her on the radio...nobody sounded like her!  1985 was a fun year for music over here.
